tech_specs: Another cool inflation aid. If you own an Exped packsack with purge valve (Shrink Bag, Shrink Bag Pro, Waterproof Compression bag or Waterproof Telecompression Bag) you can attach a Schnozzel to the valve and use the bag to inflate your Exped mat (generation 2010 onwards). Ideal for groups who can share one pump for all mats. Features:• Packed diameter: 4 cm • Packed height: 9 cm • TWeight: 25 g • TProduct contents: Schnozzel Pumpbag : reusable plastic zip-bag packaging• TWarranty: 5 years
